@startuml
title Robot Motion Simulator - Component Diagram
top to bottom direction
hide empty members

component "App" as App

component "Config Manager" as ConfigManager
component "Config Parser & Saver" as ConfigParser
component "Visualization\n(Grid + Robot Render)" as Visualization
component "GUI" as GUI
component "Physics Engine" as Physics
component "Robot Controls" as RobotControls
component "Settings Manager" as SettingManager
component "Communication Module" as CommunicationModule
' --- App as orchestrator ---
App --> SettingManager : manages settings
App --> ConfigManager : loads config
App --> GUI
App --> Physics : simulation tick
App --> CommunicationModule : handle communication with physical robot
' --- Config components ---
ConfigParser <--> ConfigManager : load/save config

' --- GUI interaction ---
GUI --> RobotControls : user input
Visualization --> GUI : render output
' --- Physics + Visualization ---
RobotControls --> Physics : motor/command input
Physics --> Visualization : updated robot pose

@enduml
